data.description: Picture yourself here! This immaculate three-bedroom, two-and a half bath gem comes complete with a spacious study and large game room. Located in a highly desirable neighborhood this property is the definition of move-in ready. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan with abundant natural light. The living area is perfect for relaxing and entertaining, while the study offers a quiet space for remote work or creativity. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances and ample counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. The bedrooms are generously sized, with the primary suite offering an en-suite bath. Take a walk to the nearby park or step into the beautiful backyard. With no direct back neighbors and a patio complete with a retractable awning you can relax in privacy. The full house generator will ensure you are never left in the dark during unexpected power outages. Schedule your showing today and make this your home sweet home.
